abstract: >-
  An explorable set of interactive, browser-based tutorials on psychophysics and
  decision-making — signal detection theory, psychometrics, scaling and appearance,
  methods of manipulation, and Bayesian inference — combining short explanations with
  live, editable code that runs in the browser.
keywords:
  - psychophysics
  - decision-making
  - signal detection theory
  - Bayesian inference
  - interactive tutorials
  - teaching
repository-code: "https://github.com/tbalsdon/psychophysical-choose-your-own-adventure"
url: "https://tbalsdon.github.io/psychophysical-choose-your-own-adventure/"
license: CC-BY-4.0
version: "1.0.0"
date-released: "2026-07-08"
